<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/1580873-i-finished-this-book-puzzled-is-etsuko-is">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[I finished this book puzzled. Is Etsuko is Sachiko? But that doesn't go well with times, since she's pregnant at that time, and the born girl is too young to be Niki. And if all the time the narrator is Sachiko, then why does she mention Jiro as her previous husband to her daughter Niki? A beuatiful book, that left me puzzled. <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
