<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">A Pale View of Hills is most interesting and Never Let Me Go if you are young. <br/><br/>An Artist of the Floating World, The Remains of the Day for older peopl<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">A Pale View of Hills is most interesting and Never Let Me Go if you are young. <br /><br />An Artist of the Floating World, The Remains of the Day for older people.<br /><a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
