        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1168048673" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6053061809812945697">My first Ishiguro. This is such a quaint and quiet novel. Inane to the point of enjoyability. I look forward to more monotony. </span>

